OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,F"Few escaped here with their lives":
OL,7,FCorrespondent John Ray reported from
OL,8,FKfar Aza on October 10 2023, where
OL,9,FHamas killed men, women and children
OL,10,Fin their beds
OL,12,FIt had been "a little piece of
OL,13,Fparadise", according to one survivor.
OL,14,FBut when we saw Kfar Aza, it was a
OL,15,Fscene straight from hell.
OL,17,FITV News cameraman Mark Nelson and I
OL,18,Fwere among the first journalists
OL,19,Finside.
