OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,FThere was gunfire close by. Israeli
OL,7,Fsoldiers were on alert. The battle
OL,8,Fwasn't entirely over.
OL,10,FBodies of Hamas fighters lay along the
OL,11,Froadside. More were stretched out
OL,12,Fbetween the ruined houses, decomposing
OL,13,Fin the sun.
OL,15,FIt had taken the Israeli army two days
OL,16,Fto recapture the village. What they
OL,17,Fdiscovered was a massacre.
OL,19,FThere was cold fury in the voice of
OL,20,FMajor General Itai Veruv.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
