OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,F"Door to door, room by room, family by
OL,7,Ffamily, people killed in their
OL,8,Fprotection room, or their apartments,"
OL,9,Fhe told me.
OL,11,FLike every Israeli, Kfar Aza's
OL,12,Fresidents had been taken by surprise
OL,13,Fthat Saturday morning of October 7.
OL,15,FBreakfasts uneaten. Coffee undrunk.
OL,17,FNow their bodies were being loaded `
OL,18,Fwith as much care as the mortuary
OL,19,Fteams could muster - into the back of
OL,20,Fa lorry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
