OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,FI counted perhaps a dozen; and watched
OL,7,Fas more were carried out from a badly
OL,8,Fburnt house.
OL,10,FClose to the village centre, a neat
OL,11,Frow of black body bags had been placed
OL,12,Fon the ground.
OL,14,FIn one house I tripped over a corpse
OL,15,Fpartially covered by debris.
OL,17,FOutside another, the body of a woman
OL,18,Flay under a blanket. Someone had
OL,19,Fthought to offer her at least a little
OL,20,Fdignity in death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
