OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,FHers was among the many images Mark
OL,7,Frecorded that were too upsetting to
OL,8,Fbroadcast.
OL,10,FIn the confusion and anger, lurid
OL,11,Fstories circulated of decapitation,
OL,12,Fand of babies murdered. They were
OL,13,Fproved false. But the truth was
OL,14,Fnightmarish enough.
OL,16,FThe civilian death toll was later put
OL,17,Fat 46. The youngest, 14 years old.
OL,18,FSome of the victims were reportedly
OL,19,Ffound with their hands bound.
