OL,3,CHow October 7 saw Kfar Aza kibbutz
OL,4,Cbecome 'scene straight from hell'
OL,6,F"We need the world to give us enough
OL,7,Ftime to win this war, because we must
OL,8,Ffinish the terrorists in Gaza," one
OL,9,Ftold me.
OL,11,FI wonder now if he imagined that a
OL,12,Fyear on, the war in Gaza would be
OL,13,Funfinished. Or that the human cost
OL,14,Fwould be so appalling, getting on for
OL,15,Fone thousand Palestinians dead for
OL,16,Fevery civilian victim of Kfar Aza.
OL,18,FA year ago, few imagined an Israel at
OL,19,Fwar in Lebanon and in a high-stakes
OL,20,Fshoot-out with Iran too.
